\tx pas              tempu do'e  kii anan   se   bibuu     ne hei     bibi    m'ata  tuma manu    kai-hitu ne'i/        
\orth pas              tembu do'e  kii ana -n se   bibi-buu  ne hei     bibi    m'ata  tuma manu    kai-hitu ne'i         
\glm pas              waktu ada   orang DIM -N satu gembala   FOC tunggu  kambing intip  biasa burung  tujuh    ini      
\gle at the same time time  EXIST person DIM -N one  goatherd  FOC wait    goat    spy    accustomed bird    seven    PRX
\glp ao mesmo tempo   tempo EXIST pessoa DIM -N um   pastor    FOC esperar cabrito espiar costumado pássaro sete     PRX 
\glt iha tempu ne'e   tempu iha   ema DIM -N ida  bibi-atan maka hein    bibi    hafuhu toman manu    hitu     ne'e      
\tlm pas waktu itu ada seorang anak gembala kambing yg sedang gembala kambing yang mengetahui tujuh burung itu           
\tle at the same time there was also a young goatherd looking after his goats, who saw the seven pigeons                 
\tlp ao mesmo tempo estava também um jovem pastor que estava a guardar os seus cabritos, e ele viu os sete pombos        
\tlt pas tempu ema bibi-atan oan ida mak he'in bibi hafuhu toman manu-pumbu hitu ne'e                                    
\dt 06/Apr/2005                                                                                                         
 

